data.description:
Nestled on an expansive .66-acre lot, this luxurious residence embodies the perfect blend of sophistication and comfort, offering a lifestyle that redefines contemporary living. Featuring a distinctive 3-car side entry garage that seamlessly complements the architectural elegance. The outdoor space is a true haven for both relaxation and entertainment, boasting a captivating fireplace on the generous covered patio. Imagine cozy evenings spent under the stars, enjoying the warmth of the fire with loved ones.
Step into the heart of this home, where every detail has been meticulously crafted to perfection. The gourmet island kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, seamlessly flowing into the attached breakfast area and family room—a central gathering space designed for creating cherished memories. The adjacent light-filled sunroom adds an extra touch of tranquility, inviting the outdoors in and providing a serene space for relaxation.
Indulge in the luxury of the owner's suite, where the expansive bedroom offers a private retreat. The ensuite bathroom is a spa-like haven, featuring a central jetted tub surrounded by opulent finishes. The walk-in shower, with its multiple shower heads, offers a rejuvenating experience, making every day feel like a getaway. The enormous walk-in closet ensures that your wardrobe is housed in style, providing ample space for even the most discerning fashion enthusiast.
Beyond the exquisite interiors, step outside to discover the lavish outdoor kitchen area in its own enclosure, preplumbed with propane and power, ready for you to add a grill and other outdoor kitchen equipment. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends or enjoying a quiet evening meal with the family, this space is designed to elevate your culinary experiences to new heights.
This residence effortlessly combines timeless elegance with modern functionality, creating a home where every detail has been carefully considered.
